# Keynavish
# https://github.com/jordansissel/keynav/blob/master/keynav.pod

# Set startup grid
ctrl+semicolon start, grid 3x3

# grid navigation — 3x3 grid via number keys
1 grid 3x3,cell-select 1x3
2 grid 3x3,cell-select 2x3
3 grid 3x3,cell-select 3x3
4 grid 3x3,cell-select 1x2
5 grid 3x3,cell-select 2x2
6 grid 3x3,cell-select 3x2
7 grid 3x3,cell-select 1x1
8 grid 3x3,cell-select 2x1
9 grid 3x3,cell-select 3x1
0 history-back

# letter grid navigation — g to toggle on/off
g grid-nav toggle,grid 6x6

# TODO use clear cmd then efine all buildings, even if using defaults, best for quick reference.
# Future: macro recording
# q record ~/.keynav_macros
# shift+at playback
# Future: dedicated click keys, cursorzoom, windowzoom remaps
